      <title>为什么你需要身处硅谷</title>
      <link>https://linguage.github.io/naval/zh/why-you-need-to-be-in-silicon-valley.zh/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 17 Jan 2010 20:41:15 +0000</pubDate>
